column5: new here to the community introing myself hoping to learn from the forum got back into fishing after a few years off fish a lot down at the rouge marsh and around north frontenac rob
Welcome Rob, hope we can help
Welcome Rob  Lived in Scarborough my whole life. Spent tons of time fishing at the Rouge marsh when I was a kid. Actually caught my first ever fish from there (A perch). Fun times
I pretty much learned to fish on the rouge... Welcome aboard .
thanks to all for the welcomes
